{
  "texts": [
    "There was also a notable difficulty in discerning the context and intent behind queries, leading to misaligned or irrelevant responses [11].",
    "Efforts to address these challenges included the introduction of more rigorous data filtering and validation mechanisms [5,30,31].",
    "However, these solutions often faced limitations in their scope and effectiveness, unable to fully resolve the issue of accuracy [5,30].",
    "The problem was further compounded in scenarios requiring the retrieval of advanced or specialized information, where even slight inaccuracies could have significant implications [32].",
    "Additionally, the sheer volume of data processed by LLMs made manual verification impractical, necessitating the development of automated accuracy assessment methods [33,34]."
  ]
}